  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ce291163126e1574e84b6d226f7d8ae1, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  txtContent: {fileID: 1603425481}
  txtTitle: {fileID: 0}
  contents:
  - "Ch\u1EA5t l\xE0 v\u1EADt li\u1EC7u c\u1EA5u t\u1EA1o n\xEAn v\u1EADt th\u1EC3.
    M\u1ED7i ch\u1EA5t \u0111\u1EC1u c\xF3 nh\u1EEFng t\xEDnh ch\u1EA5t ri\xEAng."
  - "T\xEDnh ch\u1EA5t v\u1EADt l\xED\r\n\r\nTr\u1EA1ng th\xE1i, m\xE0u s\u1EAFc,
    m\xF9i v\u1ECB, nhi\u1EC7t \u0111\u1ED9 n\xF3ng ch\u1EA3y/s\xF4i, kh\u1ED1i l\u01B0\u1EE3ng
    ri\xEAng, t\xEDnh tan..."
  - "T\xEDnh ch\u1EA5t ho\xE1 h\u1ECDc\r\n\r\nKh\u1EA3 n\u0103ng bi\u1EBFn \u0111\u1ED5i
    th\xE0nh ch\u1EA5t kh\xE1c (ch\xE1y, ph\xE2n hu\u1EF7, t\xE1c d\u1EE5ng v\u1EDBi
    axit...)"
  - "Ch\u1EA5t tinh khi\u1EBFt: ch\u1EC9 g\u1ED3m m\u1ED9t ch\u1EA5t duy nh\u1EA5t,
    c\xF3 t\xEDnh ch\u1EA5t nh\u1EA5t \u0111\u1ECBnh.\r\nH\u1ED7n h\u1EE3p: g\u1ED3m
    nhi\u1EC1u ch\u1EA5t tr\u1ED9n l\u1EABn, t\xEDnh ch\u1EA5t thay \u0111\u1ED5i
    t\xF9y th\xE0nh ph\u1EA7n."
